    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Powerful demigods, like deities and their avatars, are sometimes larger than life. You become Large (if you were already Large, you remain Large but grow a bit larger within the size category). While you are Large, you gain a reach of 10 feet, you have Advantage on Strength checks and Strength saving throws, and your weapon attacks and Unarmed Strikes deal an extra [[/r 1d4]] damage on a hit. In exchange, you have Disadvantage on Dexterity checks and Dexterity saving throws.</p><p>As an action, you can shrink back to your original size to appear closer to a more typical mortal. You remain that way until you use another action to return to your new larger size.</p>",
